- Conditions
General conditions regarding Brawl Legend bot are under this topic.

1. Our terms and conditions apply to each and every user of Brawl Legend Bot.
2. By adding Brawl Legend in your server, you agree to these terms of service and the future terms which we may add after a notice.
- Terms of Use

1. The client must not resell any component of the bot.
2. Intentional command spam or attempts to crash the bot should not be made.
3. Brawl Legend should not be used in Bot spam servers which cause command spam.
4. Brawl Legend Team reserves the rights to prohibit any server or user from using Brawl Legend.
5. The client is responsible for any violation caused by them.
6. We have the rights to update terms of service anytime with a notice in the support server.
- Terms of Use (Global Chat)
Brawl Legend Team, reserves the rights to prohibit any user or any server from using global chat feature if they fail to comply with our rules. Rules will be pinned in global chat channel once chat is activated.

1. Servers must use an appropiate server name.
2. You must not use global chat for fraudulent activities or advertising.
3. Ratelimits can be imposed on servers which cause overload in the global chat.
4. Brawl Legend team can delete any messages from global chat which we may find inappropiate, they do not necessarily have to violate our rules.
5. Other basic chat rules mentioned in the pinned rules embed must be followed.
